What is React?
Reat is a JavaScript library for building interfaces.
Has at least one component (root component).
Uses Virtual DOM, increases speed for better user interface.
There'll always be something new to learn. The best way to learn a language is to build something with it.

Requirements: HTML, CSS & JavaScript
Coding Addict - Javascript Nuggets

TERMINAL:
PWD - Full pathname to current working directory.
LS - List of Directories
ls -a - hidden folders
MKDIR - Create a Directory/Folder
CD foldername - Change a directory
cd .. - navigate to parent / one level up
Clear - clear console
Arrow key up/down - previous commands
